thread.title: baybikin

author: baybikin
title: baybikin
text: Excellent service. Excellent products. What more can I say? We are really delighted with all the Hoselink products we have bought to date. The hose reel is so much easier to pull out and put back than the cheaper version it replaced, and the fittings click together so securely we know there is no chance of them coming apart accidently. There's a couple more things on our wish list for the future, so you'll hear from us again.
